WEBVTT

00:07:29.784 --> 00:07:33.658
I went from it being
the religion of my parents,

00:07:33.682 --> 00:07:35.570
something I was inheriting,

00:07:35.594 --> 00:07:41.951
to something I was now
going to learn about deliberately.

00:07:42.264 --> 00:07:45.598
CA: Was there a moment
where you just consciously said,

00:07:45.622 --> 00:07:47.993
"This is going to be a core
part of my identity?"

00:07:48.017 --> 00:07:49.650
DM: There was.

00:07:49.674 --> 00:07:53.650
It happened around when I was 17,

00:07:53.674 --> 00:07:55.481
two years after this process,

00:07:55.505 --> 00:07:58.916
after reading Malcolm X
and studying the Quran.

00:07:58.940 --> 00:08:03.114
And it was then that I decided
to wear a hijab,